Package: ST403climr
Type: Package
Date: 2023-12-14
Title: Analyse and Plot the Latest Global and Hemispheric Climate Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Keefe", "Murphy", email="keefe.murphy@mu.ie", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads the latest climate data from NASA at monthly, quarterly, and yearly intervals. Performs basic modelling of said data and creates nice plots of temperature anomalies over time.
